### Get my notifications
GET http://localhost:5000/api/notifications/my/all
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get unread count
GET http://localhost:5000/api/notifications/my/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Mark single notification as read
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/notifications/NOTIFICATION_ID_HERE/read
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Mark multiple notifications as read
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/notifications/mark-multiple/read
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notificationIds": ["ID1", "ID2", "ID3"]
}

### Mark all notifications as read
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/notifications/mark-all/read
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Delete a notification
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/notifications/NOTIFICATION_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Delete all notifications
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/notifications/all/notifications
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get user notifications (public)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/notifications/user/USER_ID_HERE
